OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782479951
OL,3,CPilot dies after light aircraft
OL,4,Ccrashes near Dunkeswell Airfield
OL,6,FEmergency services are responding to a
OL,7,Ffatal aircraft crash near Dunkeswell
OL,8,Fairfield in East Devon.
OL,10,FPolice say the pilot ` believed to be
OL,11,Fa woman in her 40s ` was pronounced
OL,12,Fdead at the scene.
OL,14,FNobody else was on board at the time.
OL,16,FDevon and Somerset Fire Service has
OL,17,Fconfirmed that three appliances are at
OL,18,Fthe scene near Dunkeswell Aerodrome,
OL,19,Fafter a report of a light aircraft
OL,20,Fcrashing at around 10 o'clock.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
