CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782479951
OL,3,CPilot dies after light aircraft
OL,4,Ccrashes near Dunkeswell Airfield
OL,6,FThe air ambulance also attended the
OL,7,Fscene.
OL,9,FPolice say the incident is 'ongoing'
OL,10,Fand they are continuing to work with
OL,11,FThe Air Accident Investigation Branch.
OL,13,FSuperintendent Jo Arundale said: "We
OL,14,Fwill be working closely with The Air
OL,15,FAccident Investigation Branch to
OL,16,Fthoroughly investigate the
OL,17,Fcircumstances surrounding the crash
OL,18,Fthis morning.
OL,26,@uD@bOU
