PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782479951
OL,3,CPilot dies after light aircraft
OL,4,Ccrashes near Dunkeswell Airfield
OL,6,F"We recognise it is a very sad
OL,7,Fincident and we are appealing to the
OL,8,Fpublic not to speculate regarding the
OL,9,Fcrash.
OL,11,F"Furthermore, we would like to ask
OL,12,Fanybody who may have relevant footage
OL,13,Fto get in touch with us and not to
OL,14,Fpost it online.
OL,16,F"Our thoughts are with the friends and
OL,17,Ffamily of the person involved."
OL,19,FA spokesperson for the South Western
OL,20,FAmbulance Service NHS Foundation Trust
OL,21,F(SWASFT) said:
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@_O]
