OL,3,CPilot dies after light aircraft
OL,4,Ccrashes near Dunkeswell Airfield
OL,6,F"We were called at 10:01hrs on Friday
OL,7,F26 June to an incident near Honiton.
OL,8,FWe sent a double-crewed land
OL,9,Fambulance, an air ambulance, a
OL,10,Fhazardous area response team, an
OL,11,Foperations officer and a responding
OL,12,Fofficer to the scene."
